      • normalize

        public List<Field> normalize(String input)
        Normalizes content by taking a string as an input. The string is the raw content sent by the device.

        It could be anything, from a json string to xml content to raw encoded binary.

        The manifest program must know what to do with it.

        Parameters:
        input - a string containing the content to normalize.
        Returns:
        a list of normalized fields.
